A comic book style illustration showing a crowd of excited cartoon characters wearing colorful trendy clothes, all rushing frantically toward a giant glowing portal or doorway that reveals nothing but empty white space inside. The characters have exaggerated expressions of anticipation and FOMO, pushing and climbing over each other. Some are carrying laptops and early smartphones. The scene has bold black outlines, dynamic action lines, halftone dot patterns, and vibrant pop colors typical of mid-2000s comic aesthetics. The empty portal contrasts sharply with the chaotic energy of the crowd, creating visual irony.
